Name: <tc>Stefanplast Pet Carrier Mini Gulliver, For Birds & Small Pets</tc>
Description:
Stefanplast Pet Carrier Mini Gulliver, For Birds & Small Pets 


A handy and versatile carrier ideal for small birds or rodents.
It is provided with a practical handle and a transparent upper lid that can be opened. 
The numerous holes on the lid guarantee correct inside aeration and its transparency allow the light to enter more easily.


Size:40x30x24 cm

Name: Zolux Small Animal Black Harness & Lead
Description: This new range of "Casual" leashes and harnesses for small animals is designed for pet rabbits, guinea pigs, ferrets and rats, either young or adult. The set includes a basic harness and leash made of durable nylon – perfect for daily walks. The harness can be adjusted to fit your animal's neck and chest, and it fastens with a clip. The leash has a metal snap hook and is 120cm long.
